title: In The Mood - Patrick Dempsey
description:
Movie Description
This teenage comedy for adults tells the true story of the unlikely hero the tabloids dubbed "The Woo Woo Kid." Husbands and the law couldn&#039;t quite approve of Wisecarver&#039;s antics with older women. But the older women couldn&#039;t resist.

Credits 
Cast: Patrick Dempsey 
Director: Phil Alden Robinson 

Synopsis
Based on a true story about a 14-year-old kid who seduces two older women. The first to succumb to his charms is a 21-year old mother who he eventually marries. The second is a neighbor of his who he meets in a rather unusual way.
